Usage: get_propagated_clock [-help] [-clock <clock_list>] [-pin <pin_list>]
                            [> <filename>]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-clock <clock_list>     # One or more clock waveforms for which you want to
                        # retrieve the clock propagation mode information
                        # (string, optional)
-pin <pin_list>         # One or more pins or ports for which you want to
                        # retrieve the clock propagation mode information
                        # (string, optional)
> <filename>            # Name of a file in which to save the report
                        # (redirect_operator, optional)